&lt;p&gt;The pattern followed is: In BDFH : JLNP B + 2 = D; D + 2 = F; F + 2 = H &amp;amp; H + 2 = J; J + 2 = L; L + 2 = N, N + 2 = P&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Based on the same fact,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RTVX &amp;rarr; R + 2 = T; T + 2 = V; V + 2 = X&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now, X + 2 = Z; Z + 2 = B; B + 2 = D; D + 2 = F&lt;/p&gt;
Thus ZBDF is the answer.

&lt;p&gt;Let the number be &amp;lsquo;x&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When a number is increased by 24, it becomes 110% of itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x + 24 = 110% of x&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x + 24 = 1.1x&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x = 24/0.1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;x = 240&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;there4; x = 240&lt;/p&gt;

